### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/agent

### base
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search/search?query=example

### base
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search/health

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/health

### Get Available MCP Tools
GET {{apiUrl}}/tools

### Simple Chat Request
POST {{apiUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userMessage": "Hello, can you help me?",
  "conversationHistory": null,
  "model": "default"
}

### Chat with Model Specified
POST {{apiUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userMessage": "What's the weather like today?",
  "conversationHistory": null,
  "model": "gpt-4"
}

### Chat with Conversation History
POST {{apiUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userMessage": "What did I just ask you about?",
  "conversationHistory": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Tell me about the weather"
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I'd be happy to help with weather information!"
    }
  ]
}

### Test MCP Tool Usage (Facebook Example)
