### Test with Complex Request
POST {{apiUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userMessage": "Can you help me with multiple tasks: 1) Check my notifications, 2) Tell me a joke, 3) What's 2+2?",
  "conversationHistory": null,
